s=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做錯事，所以要珍惜愛你既人"},{"pid":"d5e429425c4eb939bc30360b997f5baa2f720b33","tid":146563,"uid":36700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:54:06.000Z","msg":"一句冇feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13784af3b32b30e219f6a69cd03cee2a2b7207b","tid":146563,"uid":37231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一句冇feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n為何戀愛可以當做吸過半支煙<br />\n隨時一句失去感覺我的天～<br />\n你追人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"}]}